Subject:  )  Does Motif work with XR? XR?

	Motif . is based on XR.
	Motif ., available in source form from OSF as of August , uses 
the "vanilla" XR Intrinsics, where "vanilla" means "with just a few 
patches"; the file fix-osf which OSF distributes is obsoleted by MIT's patches 
-.  The file fix-osf-.. distributed with the .. version or its 
subsequent modification needs to be applied after MIT fix-, though.

	Motif .. to .. will work with XR if XR is compiled with
-DMOTIFBC; .. and later should work with the vanilla R, although there are 
some known new geometry-management problems.
	
